<br>
(Unresisted spell damage x 2) +<br>
(Unresisted spell damage x Random focus item multiplier)<br>
---------------------------------------<br>
Total Damage from Crit.<br>
<br>
I ask because I wonder if this is intended or a mistake by VI. Imo, it makes more sense to double all the damage done, including focus items, in a crit.  That would make the max damage from a crit == 2760.  It would also up the average crit by 115.<br>
<br>
Not sure if I am correct on this, but after quite a bit of experience, it has me curious.<br>
<br>
Fenani<br>
Rodcet Nife <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/useriena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Seriena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 405<br> <font color=#333399>(6/19/02 8:42:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27650.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spell Casting Fury Crit Damage Cap?</span><hr size=1> I think my highest crit with focus so far is 2292 so I would tend to believe that your math is right (crit + random focus multiplier on base spell dmg). However, I don't think the crits should work on the focus items. It's an added bonus to our base spells. <p><br><br><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=117440" TARGET="_NEW">Seriena,</A> 60 druid<br>
<A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=185839" TARGET="_NEW">Joolz,</A> 58 Monk<br>
<A HREF=http://www.soldiers-of-light.net/>Soldiers of Light</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uscirocco.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Scirocco</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>FAQ/Index Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 5291<br> <font color=#333399>(6/19/02 11:06:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27650.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spell Casting Fury Crit Damage Cap?</span><hr size=1> <b>It's an added bonus to our base spells. </b><br>
<br>
